These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, zombie, family, time-travel
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, snowmobile, airplane
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the snowmobile##2
6. the person watching time-travel movies is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | western     | family | zombie |
| Transport     | jet-ski     | snowmobile | airplane  | scooter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, country, house, r&b
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, train, motorbike
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the fan of house is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | country    | r&b     | house  |
| Transport     | boat    | train | quad-bike | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient, country, trance
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, hedgehog, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
2. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the fan of trance##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country   | hip-hop  | trance |
| Pet           | goldfish | hamster | hedgehog | ferret  |

