.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, drawing, magic-tricks, baking
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, turkish, american, canadian
1. the canadian is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is writing and the american##2
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
4. the american is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the colombian is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | drawing | writing | baking | magic-tricks  |
| Nationality   | turkish  | colombian   | canadian  | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, tea, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, dancing, fishing, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | water   | tea | cola    |
| Hobby      | dancing | gardening | fishing       | board-games |

