.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, almond-milk, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, van, helicopter, scooter
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the scooter and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the helicopter and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up | almond-milk | sprite | water |
| Transport   | van | ship  | helicopter    | scooter  |

