.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, chinese, turkish, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, subway, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the colombian##1
2. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the turkish is between the chinese and the russian##2
5. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the tram and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | colombian | russian | turkish | chinese     |
| Transport     | car | trike  | subway   | tram |

