.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, cooking, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire, adventure, romance
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | singing | cooking | writing | rock-climbing   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | adventure | fantasy      | romance |

