.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, hamster, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, handball, rowing, cycling
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the frog is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | frog   | hamster      | rabbit      |
| Sport   | handball     | rowing | sailing | cycling |

