.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, rock, techno, funk
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, german, french, mexican
1. the polish is on the right of the german##1
2. the fan of techno is between the mexican and the german##2
3. the fan of rock is the german##1
4. the french is on the left of the german##1
5. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | rock | techno      | funk   |
| Nationality   | french  | german    | polish | mexican |

