.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, collecting, rock-climbing, traveling
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, subway, roller, bus
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the bus is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
6. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | cooking | rock-climbing | traveling    | collecting      |
| Transport   | roller       | bus       | subway | boat |

