.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, french, brazilian, chinese
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, mouse, turtle
1. the french is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is the pakistani##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the french##3
5. the brazilian is on the left or right of the chinese##3
6. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the chinese##3
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | brazilian  | chinese | french |
| Pet           | mouse     | turtle | hedgehog    | goat     |

