.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, orange, grapefruit, pumpkin
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, pilot, chef, firefighter
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the pilot##3
2. the pilot is on the right of the chef##1
3. the person eating orange is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the pilot is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | orange  | asparagus | pumpkin  | grapefruit      |
| Job    | firefighter | accountant | chef | pilot |

