4. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
6. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games | video-games | gardening | hiking |
| Music-Genre   | salsa     | funk       | pop   | d&b      |

