.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, almond-milk, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, water-polo, surfing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | hot-chocolate     | almond-milk          | water |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | water-polo | rugby | surfing  |

 